<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="588" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1437,258,967]" pageId="4" pageNumber="588">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,297,258,283]" pageId="4" pageNumber="588">Description.</emphasis>
Vertex brownish yellow, with pair of milky yellow preapical spots medially. Eyes black (Figs D, E). Face brownish yellow (Fig. F). Pronotum pale yellow, with central part translucent, revealing three large black spots on mesonotum (Fig. D). Scutellum with apex and basal triangles black (Fig. D). Fore wing yellowish white, clavus with continuous dark brown vitta parallel to suture (Figs D, 
<number box="[902,917,367,391]" pageId="4" pageNumber="588" value="8.0">8</number>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1437,258,967]" box="[199,975,402,427]" pageId="4" pageNumber="588">
Male abdominal apodemes small, not surpassing 
<number box="[750,762,402,427]" pageId="4" pageNumber="588" value="3.0">3</number>
rd sternite (
<figureCitation box="[892,961,402,427]" captionStart="FIGURES 8 – 15" captionStartId="3.[151,264,1889,1912]" captionTargetBox="[160,1402,504,1854]" captionTargetId="figure@3.[152,1435,483,1868]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURES 8 – 15. Arboridia ochracea Song &amp; Li, sp. nov.: 8, Fore wing; 9, Abdominal apodemes; 10, Pygofer lobe, lateral view; 11, Subgenital plate; 12, Style; 13, Aedeagus, lateral view; 14, Aedeagus, ventral view; 15, Connective." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/238917/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="588">
Fig. 
<number box="[945,961,403,427]" pageId="4" pageNumber="588" value="9.0">9</number>
</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1437,258,967]" pageId="4" pageNumber="588">
<emphasis box="[199,368,438,463]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="588">Male genitalia</emphasis>
: Pygofer dorsal appendage simple, shallowly bifurcate at apex (
<figureCitation box="[1135,1223,438,463]" captionStart="FIGURES 8 – 15" captionStartId="3.[151,264,1889,1912]" captionTargetBox="[160,1402,504,1854]" captionTargetId="figure@3.[152,1435,483,1868]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURES 8 – 15. Arboridia ochracea Song &amp; Li, sp. nov.: 8, Fore wing; 9, Abdominal apodemes; 10, Pygofer lobe, lateral view; 11, Subgenital plate; 12, Style; 13, Aedeagus, lateral view; 14, Aedeagus, ventral view; 15, Connective." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/238917/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="588">
Fig. 
<number box="[1192,1223,439,463]" pageId="4" pageNumber="588" value="10.0">10</number>
</figureCitation>
). Subgenital plate without basolateral angulate projection, with 
<number box="[660,674,475,499]" pageId="4" pageNumber="588" value="4.0">4</number>
macrosetae in oblique row and row of short rigid setae along upper margin; apical 
<number box="[326,337,511,535]" pageId="4" pageNumber="588" value="1.0">1</number>
/ 
<number box="[348,363,511,535]" pageId="4" pageNumber="588" value="3.0">3</number>
, with dark color (
<figureCitation box="[576,661,510,535]" captionStart="FIGURES 8 – 15" captionStartId="3.[151,264,1889,1912]" captionTargetBox="[160,1402,504,1854]" captionTargetId="figure@3.[152,1435,483,1868]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURES 8 – 15. Arboridia ochracea Song &amp; Li, sp. nov.: 8, Fore wing; 9, Abdominal apodemes; 10, Pygofer lobe, lateral view; 11, Subgenital plate; 12, Style; 13, Aedeagus, lateral view; 14, Aedeagus, ventral view; 15, Connective." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/238917/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="588">
Fig. 
<number box="[631,661,511,535]" pageId="4" pageNumber="588" value="11.0">11</number>
</figureCitation>
). Style long, with 
<number box="[880,894,511,535]" pageId="4" pageNumber="588" value="2.0">2</number>
sharp points at apex; preapical lobe small but distinct (
<figureCitation box="[252,338,546,571]" captionStart="FIGURES 8 – 15" captionStartId="3.[151,264,1889,1912]" captionTargetBox="[160,1402,504,1854]" captionTargetId="figure@3.[152,1435,483,1868]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURES 8 – 15. Arboridia ochracea Song &amp; Li, sp. nov.: 8, Fore wing; 9, Abdominal apodemes; 10, Pygofer lobe, lateral view; 11, Subgenital plate; 12, Style; 13, Aedeagus, lateral view; 14, Aedeagus, ventral view; 15, Connective." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/238917/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="588">
Fig. 
<number box="[307,338,547,571]" pageId="4" pageNumber="588" value="12.0">12</number>
</figureCitation>
). Aedeagus with two pairs of processes arising from apex and base of shaft respectively, basal processes short, slender and closely appressed on ventral surface of shaft, distal processes approximately same length but arising laterad of gonopore and extended posterolaterad; aedeagal shaft long, only median area slightly bent ventrad; gonopore large, apical on ventral surface; preatrium much longer than dorsal apodeme, evenly curved in lateral view (
<figureCitation box="[326,456,690,715]" captionStart="FIGURES 8 – 15" captionStartId="3.[151,264,1889,1912]" captionTargetBox="[160,1402,504,1854]" captionTargetId="figure@3.[152,1435,483,1868]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURES 8 – 15. Arboridia ochracea Song &amp; Li, sp. nov.: 8, Fore wing; 9, Abdominal apodemes; 10, Pygofer lobe, lateral view; 11, Subgenital plate; 12, Style; 13, Aedeagus, lateral view; 14, Aedeagus, ventral view; 15, Connective." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/238917/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="588">Figs 13, 14</figureCitation>
). Connective robust, broadly V-shaped (
<figureCitation box="[907,991,690,715]" captionStart="FIGURES 8 – 15" captionStartId="3.[151,264,1889,1912]" captionTargetBox="[160,1402,504,1854]" captionTargetId="figure@3.[152,1435,483,1868]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURES 8 – 15. Arboridia ochracea Song &amp; Li, sp. nov.: 8, Fore wing; 9, Abdominal apodemes; 10, Pygofer lobe, lateral view; 11, Subgenital plate; 12, Style; 13, Aedeagus, lateral view; 14, Aedeagus, ventral view; 15, Connective." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/238917/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="588">
Fig. 
<number box="[960,991,690,715]" pageId="4" pageNumber="588" value="15.0">15</number>
</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1437,258,967]" box="[199,1123,726,751]" pageId="4" pageNumber="588">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,370,726,751]" pageId="4" pageNumber="588">Measurement.</emphasis>
